             Following is a list of odds offered
today by U.K. bookmaker William Hill to win the soccer World Cup
in South Africa. The semifinals are scheduled July 6 and 7:  

 
     Spain         15-8
     Germany        2-1
     Netherlands    2-1
     Uruguay       12-1
 
